  ('dietitian-moex-08876', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-098-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關引起毒素型細菌性食物中毒之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["為革蘭氏陰性菌，潛伏期長，有腹瀉、發燒症狀", "為革蘭氏陽性菌，潛伏期短，有嘔吐症狀、不發燒", "為革蘭氏陰性菌，潛伏期短，有腹瀉症狀、不發燒", "為革蘭氏陽性菌，潛伏期長，有嘔吐、發燒症狀"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8ef415595ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0184ce20793", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098140", "c": "113", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、醫師分試 、法醫師", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-08877', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-098-da9d23a3', 'sub-dietitian-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關沙門氏菌之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["沙門氏菌在澱粉含量高的食品中繁殖情況最佳", "沙門氏菌可由動物腸管直接污染食物", "主要症狀為下痢、腹痛、寒顫、發燒", "本菌不耐熱，於60℃加熱20分鐘可被殺滅"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8ef415595ad", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0184ce20793", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098140", "c": "113", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "食品衛生與安全", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、醫師分試 、法醫師", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
